               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430821-name-797" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-797" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-797" type="surname" value="THURLOW"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-797" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN THURLOW</persName>
                  </hi>. I am butler to the Rev. Dr. John Hume Spry. He lives in York-terrace—on the 6th of July we had four spoons and two forks in the dining-room—I missed them—these are them—they are my master's.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. PRENDERGAST</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> The prisoner was not in your service? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> No.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
